extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Record Shack], a simple inventory website for your favourite vinyl records.

  h1 Music Database

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{data.record_count}
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.artist_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}